{"tid":99801,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"急求止咳方法","createTime":"2017-01-29T13:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T05:33:14.000Z","uid":10325,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc32a1b705147394892c306284eff4d3472626ef","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"每次喉嚨痛完都會一直咳，仲會持續1-2個星期咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家又開始咳了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家有咩止咳既方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34830f532fcce6aacde50fe2d60d1e75fb5d542","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"有幾次睇完私家食完藥都係止唔到咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"179efd255cc5855897c9df4524af39ffa4d9211c","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597ba32294046ce010babf13fabc48365a2dbdb0","tid":99801,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg&h=54a7916d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"785edc9844c6a6f48347f955dced18551e8506c4","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg&h=54a7916d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8529ae21c9982b9f4854fa6cb1e3cd026e7a4f21","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f30fd143f4c063934e58953317cdb32e4940539","tid":99801,"uid":22902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:12:52.000Z","msg":"認真燉橙<br />\n或者整洋蔥水同食蛇皮果"},{"pid":"7953bba1ee9bb2cb38f04363979b55bf8bc5a26a","tid":99801,"uid":44427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"含住條憤怒的香腸就唔會再咳"},{"pid":"99d3a45f3ae1170af5a24d62dc3b7d82cf0831f4","tid":99801,"uid":53800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"潤下，舒服少少咁解咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，太「結」太乾試下溝少少水"},{"pid":"cb1078851086c61db8fc5838212865a14d0b5998","tid":99801,"uid":60065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:15:40.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦屌你"},{"pid":"874d9463793c468e80a1fa9412d8436acde15450","tid":99801,"uid":24785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"燉橙"},{"pid":"c3679987d452110bfe6ef9cc0f7bb3cf4d19b50f","tid":99801,"uid":26311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F210444_6972d70e5c4f6af98785067aee1516ab.jpg&h=54a7916d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係有用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有<br />\n日日飲  一日三次當水飲<br />\n乜病都無"},{"pid":"7877f3daf3813afdab84c0bfd0a8b629a69a819f","tid":99801,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"你咳出來嘅嘢係點？痰定係透明黏液狀嘅嘢？咳嘅頻密程度？（例如：夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先咳？定係冷氣房咳得密？）不如對症下藥斷尾仲好。我睇醫生都會同佢講得比較細緻D。<br />\n利申：<br />\n一次重感冒，等醫生等得好辛苦就嚟暈咁。比咗藥我食，發燒喉痛個D好翻但係就日日不停咳，返工帶咗幾個星期口罩，返工隔一小時就不停咳，夜晚小D，訓覺又咳。枇杷露同燉橙試過一概無用。同一間醫務所睇咗三次都唔好，轉過另一間睇，開返另一隻藥，咳返D痰就好返。<br />\n另一次輕微感冒，小小燒，喉嚨小小痛，零星咳（咳黏液），食咗三日藥（有氣管藥）都未好。咁啱我阿媽又係成日咳，睇政府醫院比咗隻黃色抗敏感藥丸佢。我食埋佢食剩藥丸，幾日後好返。"},{"pid":"5663eed58ffe2d226eeb9413a8f1156081a791a3","tid":99801,"uid":70686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"戒J"},{"pid":"efe224bff7e8f877505a20e3151b1b7260030045","tid":99801,"uid":70686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"認真就睇醫生<br />\n不過預防勝於治療<br />\n問醫生la"},{"pid":"fa8f35a81ec38cdb142acddecc51295e7bd8ba0c","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>潤下，舒服少少咁解咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，太「結」太乾試下溝少少水</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5515801efd2704a0d7479401bd0228ea6cf531bb","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咳出來嘅嘢係點？痰定係透明黏液狀嘅嘢？咳嘅頻密程度？（例如：夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先咳？定係冷氣房咳得密？）不如對症下藥斷尾仲好。我睇醫生都會同佢講得比較細緻D。<br />\n利申：<br />\n一次重感冒，等醫生等得好辛苦就嚟暈咁。比咗藥我食，發燒喉痛個D好翻但係就日日不停咳，返工帶咗幾個星期口罩，返工隔一小時就不停咳，夜晚小D，訓覺又咳。枇杷露同燉橙試過一概無用。同一間醫務所睇咗三次都唔好，轉過另一間睇，開返另一隻藥，咳返D痰就好返。<br />\n另一次輕微感冒，小小燒，喉嚨小小痛，零星咳（咳黏液），食咗三日藥（有氣管藥）都未好。咁啱我阿媽又係成日咳，睇政府醫院比咗隻黃色抗敏感藥丸佢。我食埋佢食剩藥丸，幾日後好返。</blockquote><br />\n我每次病都係咁，一喉嚨痛完就一定會咳好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇完醫生都係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點做好"},{"pid":"8e4b96edb31010730d41fb9756a33ba9ba841f5b","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒J</blockquote><br />\n琴日咳緊仲打左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58897f1e5d15200eb2e08b08a5d34862c5369d6","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"做多d運動會唔會病幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？身體好弱"},{"pid":"472164c3a9da91179e998859dc897661bffa2269","tid":99801,"uid":9169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T16:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燉橙</blockquote><br />\n堅有用"},{"pid":"2a04623c7bfa0e831fec2ba3fc9e1a87bd055c7e","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>燉橙</blockquote><br />\n堅有用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce46b7bf41bcb013cadc2ca434d37938a7abb92","tid":99801,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T02:16:31.000Z","msg":"通常久咳都係感染過後氣管變得敏感<br />\n食藥可以減輕病情<br />\n不過其實無助康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aebcddd0cf3e9fd2874bb4d4f9f6ecfaf79e5a","tid":99801,"uid":28920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"紫色史立消 &times;喉嚨痛既必利痛&times; 消炎藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1354e0d94ae58bda8d1a4f1c899a2847919b93","tid":99801,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"打J時候應該唔咳"},{"pid":"02d6160f310ed33851b43648e213d7f9e95b1197","tid":99801,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常久咳都係感染過後氣管變得敏感<br />\n食藥可以減輕病情<br />\n不過其實無助康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /